data.meta_site_name: Goodman Real Estate Services Group LLC
data.text:
Eyemart Express is now open at the Market at Hilliard in Hilliard, Ohio. Eyemart Express currently has retail stores in many states across the United States. The Hilliard location joined national retailers, including Target, Old Navy, Michaels, and more. Steven Dorsky, Senior Executive/Director with Goodman Real Estate Services Group LLC, represented Eyemart Express in this transaction. Steven Dorsky, and Zachary Sogoloff, Senior Vice President of Goodman Real Estate Group LLC, represent Eyemart Express throughout most of Ohio.
